hipelago\" and the wartime bombing of Dresden before his untimely death on 10 April 1978.In the BBC documentary tribute to Vas directed by Barrie Gavin, Karel Reisz said of him that his aim was to \"inspire thought, to remind and warn\". Source: Wikidata; 01/08/2023", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2025-03-14T17:35:15.529810+11:00", "external_links": [{"id": 5043, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Vas"}], "uuid": "cd3bd6e0-4737-4d48-a738-7edd0fcafa0f", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "1798", "external_references": [{"id": 26515, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q7350581"}, {"id": 31224, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "330450"}, {"id": 31225, "source": {"name": "LOC Auth", "slug": "loc-auth"}, "source_identifier": "no2008120699"}, {"id": 31226, "source": {"name": "WorldCat", "slug": "worldcat"}, "source_identifier": "lccn-no2008120699"}], "date_modified": "2025-03-14T17:35:15.530105+11:00"}, {"id": 16162, "name": "Vincent O'Donnell", "roles_in_work": [{"id": 763663, "title": "Through a looking glass: a film on drama", "work_id": 77135, "role": "director", "role_id": 938, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 762393, "title": "A Good scheme", "work_id": 76609, "role": "director", "role_id": 938, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 856387, "title": "Open to change", "work_id": 71169, "role": "director", "role_id": 938, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 759464, "title": "Ian Chappell on cricket", "work_id": 75408, "role": "director", "role_id": 938, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2357900, "title": "The Koala", "work_id": 69440, "role": "co-director", "role_id": 959, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2374041, "title": "Museum: a living memory", "work_id": 78217, "role": "co-producer", "role_id": 915, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 1804082, "title": "Port, power and people", "work_id": 78218, "role": "producer", "role_id": 1089, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 1804457, "tit